As an IT Manager, I was amazed how often I got asked by colleagues: "What's my password, I forgot it”. This prompted me to create an app where everyone could securely store their passwords and secret notes. 
When a friend suggested expanding the app to include private Photos and Videos, I realized many people would appreciate a discreet way to keep intimate pictures hidden from their camera roll.

To enhance the app further, I added features for securely storing Contacts and Bank Accounts or Credit Cards, ensuring it includes all the sensitive data people would want to Securely Protect on their phones and tablets.

1. Security Features - I prioritized user data protection by implementing the latest software and hardware technologies from Apple:
*** All data is Hardware Encrypted using your Passcode or Touch ID/Face ID
*** Log in using Touch ID, Face ID, or a Master Password each time you launch the app
*** Data is stored locally on your device ONLY
*** Any data entered is never sent anywhere, ensuring your privacy
*** The Login Master Password set during the first launch can NOT be retrieved on request. It is ONLY stored on the user's system keychain and NO-ONE else has it - the user MUST memorise it

2. Usability Features:
*** Unlimited import and export of media
*** Photo slideshow capability for easy viewing
*** A simple, user-friendly native iOS interface
*** Sophisticated storage methods to ensure data preservation
*** A fast and responsive Media Gallery
*** Quick import from your camera roll with an option to delete the originals after importing
*** An in-app camera for capturing private moments on-the-fly
*** Auto-detection of addresses, phone numbers, and web links
*** A clean, dark incognito design for discretion and is also better for the battery life

With these features, you can enjoy peace of mind knowing your sensitive information is securely protected and easily accessible when you need it.
